description:
This is a 29 minute workout called '30 MIN PILATES | At-Home Full Body Workout (No Equipment)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: I hope you enjoy this 30-Minute Full Body Pilates Workout, designed to tone and sculpt the entire body. This at-home and no-equipment workout is perfect for our current situation of needing to stay at home. Hope you are well and staying safe. xx
